description:
It's Part 2 with special guest Mary Carey, Ex-porn actress, Model, Reality TV star, and two time Governor Candidate of California. She and Bunnie imagine what life would be like with the two of them in office together, and Mary opens up about her infertility and treatments. She also shares how she met her husband, dumped a bad ex, and what really happened after Celebrity Rehab.
